{"tid":2046232,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"狗方向六四晚會發出反對通知書","createTime":"2020-06-01T09:20:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T09:25:06.000Z","uid":211994,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1b9894d6175b2e7763e377679c2459ba42a76333","tid":2046232,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T09:20:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200601&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=61004033\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200601%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D61004033&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns84uQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=dac80b8b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200601%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D61004033&h=0a376374\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200601&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=61004033</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7pV3N3d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7pV3N3d.png&h=fd6c9982&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年是六四事件31周年，支聯會每年都會申請6月4日在維園舉行六四集會，惟警方今年藉疫情和「限聚令」實施為由，已向支持聯會發出反對通知書。<br />\n<br />\n支聯會秘書長蔡耀昌接受《蘋果》訪問時，對警方的決定表示失望和憤怒，直斥警方的決定是「完全無理由」，又指現時本港疫情已緩和，支聯會亦會做好防疫措施，但警方仍然以疫情為藉口作政治打壓，是侵犯《基本法》及《人權法》賦予市民的集會及遊行權利。"},{"pid":"b66ba0875d82e3977f948824a6b79ed7b80a963f","tid":2046232,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T09:22:45.000Z","msg":"支聯會早前已為六四集會準備Plan B，將於當晚8時，在Facebook、IG等直播悼念儀式，8時9分亦會為六四死難者默哀。他呼籲市民屆時遍地開花，在全港各處進行悼念。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，支聯會成員會以個人身份、8人一組前往維園。他強調維園並非完全封閉，個別人士亦有權進入。"},{"pid":"fd6e0eac232089b1c4d1c4e72e9c7c4c8c7181f9","tid":2046232,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T09:25:06.000Z","msg":"[行動POST]615全民放假悼念日<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2046213\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2046213</a>"}]}